{
  "stem": "27031.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And after about a few minutes he disappeared, the guy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I got up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And like father used to tell us, if you're in trouble, try and run to the Czech village.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I run straight in the middle of the night to the straight-- to the-- pardon me- to the Ch-- Czech village.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES] And I went into a barn, and lay down, fell asleep on a straw pile.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And in the morning, I wake up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I look, I got blood all over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I look here, and I got a hole in my shoulder in the front and the back.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I guess the bullet went through the back and came out through the front.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I guess the second bullet missed me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES] I presumed my brother was dead.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was laying, when I seen the blood all over, I got panicky.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I ran out to the people, the Czech people, I knew them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, uh, I knew most farmers there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I ran into the house-- or the lady was in the barn, and I approached her for some help.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said I was shot, I need a little water to wash up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she did bring me, she fed me, she kept me for about three, four-- two, three weeks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's guessing time, I really can't remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I couldn't move my hand for awhile.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But after that, after two weeks, I could move it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said, I would like you to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES] I couldn't find my father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I thought my brother is dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I went in the same village, that was called Sofievka, the town- ah, village.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sofievka-- S-O-F-I-J-E-W-I-- A approximately.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I went at night, she gave me food, that lady, which was very nice.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
